//           We are using Webpack for bundling



-----------     Workflow       -------------

1) After saved changes and pushed to Github:
        npm run-script build

2) Copy all the files generated by the code in ./dist

3) Delete all BUT FAVICON.ICO AND CNAME files inside of productionmode folder

4) Paste the files generated in ./dist

5) cd productionmode in the terminal

6) Push all the new files to gh-pages branch






-----------     Available Scripts    -------


npm start


npm run-script build